title: Chick Talks Jobim
description:
Interested in learning directly from Chick? Join the Chick Corea Academy today! Click here now: https://www.chickcoreaacademy.com/
 
Chick talks Jobim and the composer he likes to combine him with... Chick's solo piano version of "Desafinado" is the latest single off his forthcoming album, "Plays" and is available to stream now wherever you get your music!

Pre-order "Plays" here on CD or vinyl and check out exclusive offerings: https://found.ee/ChickCoreaStore

---

🎶 The brand-new Chick Corea Academy is now enrolling! Get access to LIVE weekly workshops with Chick, all of Chick's past workshops, weekly releases of rare recordings from Chick's Vault, and more! Click here to learn more: www.ChickCoreaAcademy.com  

Chick's book, "A Work in Progress", has recently been re-released! Get your copy here: bit.ly/A_Work_in_Progress
